Overseas_Himg&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;p class=&quot;img-txt-top-left&quot;&gt;OVERSEAS STUDENT&lt;/p&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/section&gt;\r\n					&lt;section&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;blue-content&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-size: 3.5vw; font-weight: 800; color: #2D3138;&quot;&gt;WHO IS THIS PAGE FOR?&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n							&lt;img src=&quot;images\\Overseas_rsc1.png&quot; alt=&quot;Overseas_rsc1&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 2vw; color: #2D3138; margin: 20px;&quot;&gt;This page is dedicated to students who are not from Singapore (Overseas Students).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/section&gt;\r\n					&lt;section&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;right_txt&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size: 3vw; font-weight: 800; text-align: left; color: #2D3138; max-width: 47%; margin-top: 60px; margin-bottom: 0;&quot;&gt;Arrival of an Overseas Student in 3 Simple Steps&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_img_container&quot;&gt;\r\n								&lt;img src=&quot;images\\Overseas_rsc2.png&quot; alt=&quot;Overseas_rsc2&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n							&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1;&quot;&gt;\r\n								&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_h&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;div class=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;\r\n										&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-size: 2vw;&quot;&gt;Arrive in Singapore&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n									&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; text-align: left; margin-left: 120px; padding-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;To arrive in Singapore, you need to be granted a short-term visit pass by ICA of Singapore and be fully vaccinated.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n								&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_h&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;div class=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;\r\n										&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-size: 2vw;&quot;&gt;Medical Check Up&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n									&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; text-align: left; margin-left: 120px; padding-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;For Overseas Students who want to study in Singapore, a medical check-up is required for the Student Pass holder to receive a medical clearance for studying in Singapore.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n								&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_h&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;div class=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;\r\n										&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-size: 2vw;&quot;&gt;Issuance of Student’s Pass&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n									&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; text-align: left; margin-left: 120px; padding-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;For your studies at UON SG, you must possess a current Student&amp;apos;s Pass granted by the Immigration &amp; Checkpoints Authority (ICA) of Singapore.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/section&gt;\r\n					&lt;section&gt;\r\n						&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size: 4vw; font-weight: 800; text-align: left; margin-left: 30px; color: #3431A6; margin-bottom: 0;&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT TO TAKE NOTE...&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n						&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 1.5vw; text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;&quot;&gt;In order for overseas students who want to collect their own Student Pass, they need to:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;blue-line&quot; style=&quot;display: flex&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;h2&gt;Pass Mandatory Medical Examination&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n							&lt;p&gt;The examination will include tests for the Human Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) and Tuberculosis. You will be denied admission and must return home at your own expense if you fail the medical examination.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;blue-line&quot; style=&quot;display: flex&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;h2&gt;Student Pass Application&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n							&lt;p&gt;Please be aware that the completion of Student&amp;apos;s Pass requirements with ICA must be done exclusively by e-appointment only at the ICA building during the validity of the Social Visit Pass/expiration date of the IPA letter, whichever is sooner.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/section&gt;\r\n					&lt;section&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;left_txt&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size: 3vw; font-weight: 800; text-align: left; color: #2D3138; max-width: 50%; margin-top: 60px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 55px;&quot;&gt;Documents Required For Medical Check-Up&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1;&quot;&gt;\r\n								&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 60px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_h&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;div class=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;\r\n										&lt;h3&gt;Passport&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n									&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 60px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;div class=&quot;overseas_info_text_container_h&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;div class=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;\r\n										&lt;h3&gt;In Principle Approval/IPA Form&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n									&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;/div&gt;\r\n								&lt;